2172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"score\": 0.8074598192380074, \"rank\": 0.23814369236763047, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group believes that the stripping of the medal winners is an important step, especially if the IOC is to maintain credibility ahead of the Paralympics set to get underway in a fortnight.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4434792948333525e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Pizzi said: \\\"We could potentially encounter the ridiculous situation where Ukrainian Paralympians, who are disabled as a result of the war, are having to compete against people that support the conflict that caused their injuries.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2500, \"end\": 2505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pizzi_(Portuguese_footballer)\", \"score\": 0.9659353520439725, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pizzi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pizzi_(Portuguese_footballer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pizzi_(Portuguese_footballer)\"}, {\"begin\": 2575, \"end\": 2584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"score\": 0.8074598192380074, \"rank\": 0.23814369236763047, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"How can the IOC and their sponsors justify this?\\\"\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2745, \"end\": 2748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4434792948333525e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The group is pessimistic of their chances, with the IOC refusing to respond to them for many months but believe that pressuring the organisation and the sponsors that fund them is crucial in holding to account an organisation that speaks often about respect from human rights.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 3062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2838, \"end\": 2841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4434792948333525e-24, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3283, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Mr Pizzi said: \\\"The IOC's supposed 'commitments' to human rights are nothing more than window dressing for an organisation that shamefully refuses to take accountability.\\\"\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3328, \"end\": 3331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\"